divs: Sighting DetailsSitting on deck and began observing numerous star-like shapes forming different patterns. At times they stayed stationary and other times seemed to form patterns that became one. We noticed these objects because of the clarity of the evening and became fascinated over there patterns and movement.The experience was enthralling and went on for approx 2 hours.After watching with binoculars, all objects just disappeared. Interesting, that I also observed three airforce jets, in the sky during this experience.
